icon glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down\"></span></button>\n<ul aria-orientation=\"vertical\" data-ajax-replace=\"/content/dam/canada/sitemenu/sitemenu-v2-en.html\" role=\"menu\">\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/jobs.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Jobs and the workplace</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/immigration-citizenship.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Immigration and citizenship</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://travel.gc.ca/\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Travel and tourism</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/business.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Business and industry</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/benefits.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Benefits</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/health.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Health</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/taxes.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Taxes</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/environment.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Environment and natural resources</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/defence.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">National security and defence</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/culture.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Culture, history and sport</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/policing.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Policing, justice and emergencies</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/transport.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Transport and infrastructure</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.international.gc.ca/world-monde/index.aspx?lang=eng\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Canada and the world</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/finance.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Money and finances</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/science.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Science and innovation</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/life-events.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Manage life events</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<nav id=\"wb-bc\" property=\"breadcrumb\"><h2 class=\"wb-inv\">You are here:</h2><div class=\"container\"><ol class=\"breadcrumb\">\n<li><a href=\"/en.html\">Canada.ca</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/travel.html\">Travel and tourism</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports.html\">Canadian passports and other travel documents</a></li>\n</ol></div></nav>\n</header>\n</div>\n</div>\n<main class=\"container\" property=\"mainContentOfPage\" resource=\"#wb-main\" typeof=\"WebPageElement\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<h1 id=\"wb-cont\" property=\"name\"><span class=\"stacked\"><span>Check our service standards</span>: <span>Canadian passports and other travel documents</span></span></h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsmediaplayer section\">\n<script>\n            function docReady(fn) {\n        // see if DOM is already available\n        if (document.readyState === \"complete\" || document.readyState === \"interactive\") {\n        // call on next available tick\n            setTimeout(fn, 1);\n        } else {\n            document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", fn);\n        }\n    }    \n\n    docReady(function() {\n\n        let customcss = document.createElement('link');\n        customcss.setAttribute('rel', 'stylesheet');\n        customcss.setAttribute('href', 'https://test.canada.ca/wayfinding-orientation-2023/css/split-h1.css');  \n        document.head.appendChild(customcss);       \n\t});\n</script>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div data-wb-jsonmanager='{\n\t\t\"url\": \"/content/dam/ircc/documents/json/data-passport-ptime.json\",\n\t\t\"name\": \"ptime\"\n\t}' id=\"jsonmanagerpassportprocessingtime\"></div>\n<p>Check the <a href=\"#service\">service standards</a> below to see approximately how long it <strong>may</strong> take us to process your application under normal circumstances. We recommend you <strong>don’t finalize any travel plans</strong> until you get your passport.</p>\n<details>\n<summary><span id=\"service\">What’s the difference between a service standard and a processing time?</span></summary>\n<p>The <strong>service standard</strong> for your application is our commitment to process your application in a certain amount of time, under normal circumstances.</p>\n<p>The <strong>processing time</strong> for your application is the actual time it takes us to process your application. We can’t tell you exactly how long it will take.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Your processing time\n      <ul>\n<li>starts once we have\n          <ul>\n<li>your application form</li>\n<li>all your supporting documents, <strong>and</strong></li>\n<li>payment of your fees</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>depends on whether your application is properly completed or not</li>\n<li>depends on how you applied</li>\n<li>depends on if we need new or additional information for your application</li>\n<li><strong>doesn’t</strong> include mailing time</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>A small number of cases may take longer\n      <ul>\n<li>if we have to ask for corrections (to your application) or new photos</li>\n<li>when we do routine verifications <strong>and security checks</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</details>\n<div class=\"wb-frmvld hidden\" id=\"ff\">\n<form>\n<div class=\"wb-fieldflow gc-font-2019\" data-wb-fieldflow='{\n            \"noForm\": true,\n            \"renderas\":\"radio\",\n            \"unhideelm\": \"#ff\",\n\t\t\t\"gcChckbxrdio\":true,\n \t\t\t\"hideelm\": \".passport-us, .passport-abroad, .passport-can-reg, .passport-can-exp, .td-reg, .certified-other, .passport-official, #korahCcrChatContainer\",\n            \"base\": { \"live\": true, \"renderas\": \"radio\", \"gcChckbxrdio\":true },\n            \"default\": { \"action\": \"addClass\", \"source\":\".passport-us, .passport-abroad, .passport-can-reg, .passport-can-exp, .td-reg, .certified-other, .passport-official\", \"class\": \"hidden\"},\n            \"reset\": { \"action\": \"addClass\", \"source\":\".passport-us, .passport-abroad, .passport-can-reg, .passport-can-exp, .td-reg, .certified-other, .passport-official, #korahCcrChatContainer\", \"class\": \"hidden\" }\n        }'>\n<p>Select an application type:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Passport\n          <div class=\"wb-fieldflow-sub\" data-wb-fieldflow='{\"reset\": {\"action\":\"addClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \"#korahCcrChatContainer\"}}'>\n<p>Where are you applying from?</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \"#korahCcrChatContainer\"}'>Canada\n                <div class=\"wb-fieldflow-sub\">\n<p>What kind of service are you applying for?</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \".passport-can-reg\"}'>Regular service</li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \".passport-can-exp\"}'>Urgent or express service</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \".passport-us\"}'>United States</li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \".passport-abroad\"}'>Outside Canada and the United States</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \".td-reg\"}'>Refugee travel document or certificate of identity</li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \".passport-official\"}'>Official (special or diplomatic) passport </li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\", \"source\": \".certified-other\"}'>Certified true copy of a passport or other travel document\n         \n        </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</form>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 passport-can-reg\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<h2 id=\"passport-can-reg\">Service standards for regular passport applications submitted in Canada</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div class=\"row wb-eqht-grd\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6 hght-inhrt\">\n<div class=\"well hght-inhrt\">\n<p class=\"h3 mrgn-tp-0\">Submitted in person at a passport office (Service Canada Centre – Passport Services) or Service Canada Centre that offers 10-day processing</p>\n<br/><p class=\"h1 text-center\">10<sup id=\"fn1-rf\"><a class=\"fn-lnk\" href=\"#fn1\"><span class=\"wb-inv\">Footnote </span>*</a></sup></p>\n<p class=\"h3 text-center\">business days</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6 hght-inhrt\">\n<div class=\"well hght-inhrt\">\n<p class=\"h3 mrgn-tp-0\">Submitted in person at a regular Service Canada Centre, a Service Canada Scheduled Outreach Site that offers passport services, by mail or online</p>\n<br/><p class=\"h1 text-center\">20<sup id=\"fn2-rf\"><a class=\"fn-lnk\" href=\"#fn1\"><span class=\"wb-inv\">Footnote </span>*</a></sup></p>\n<p class=\"h3 text-center\">business days</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<aside class=\"wb-fnote\" role=\"note\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\" id=\"fn\">Footnotes</h2>\n<dl>\n<dt>Footnote *</dt>\n<dd id=\"fn1\">\n<p>This <strong>doesn’t</strong> include mailing time. We aren’t liable for any losses if we can’t deliver your passport in time.</p>\n<p class=\"fn-rtn\"><a href=\"#fn1-rf\"><span class=\"wb-inv\">Return to footnote </span>*<span class=\"wb-inv\"> referrer</span></a></p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n</aside>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsgeneric_base_html mwsgeneric-base-html parbase\">\n<span data-incl-name=\"passport-cas-en\"></span>\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-bttm-sm\">Check your application status</h3>\n<p>Answer a few questions to find out how to check your application status.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/check-passport-travel-document-application.html\">Learn how to check the status of your application</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsgeneric_base_html mwsgeneric-base-html parbase\">\n<span data-incl-name=\"passport-ss-refund-en\"></span>\n<p class=\"h3\">If we don’t meet our service standards</p>\n<p>You may be eligible for a partial refund of some of your fees under the <a href=\"https://laws-lois.justice.gc.ca/eng/acts/S-8.4/\">Service Fees Act</a>. Refunds are processed automatically. Learn <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/fees/passport-travel-document-refunds.html\">what refunds you might be eligible for</a>.</p>\n<p>Learn more about our policies for fee remissions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/mandate/policies-operational-instructions-agreements/remissions-policy-service-fees-act.html\">Departmental Remission Policy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/mandate/policies-operational-instructions-agreements/remissions-policy-service-fees-act/passport-subordinate-remission-policy.html\">Passport Subordinate Remission Policy</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 passport-can-exp\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<h2 id=\"passport-can-exp\">Service standards for urgent or express passport applications submitted in Canada</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div class=\"row wb-eqht-grd\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6 hght-inhrt\">\n<div class=\"well hght-inhrt\">\n<p class=\"h3 mrgn-tp-0\">Urgent pick-up</p>\n<p class=\"h2\">By end of next business day</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6 hght-inhrt\">\n<div class=\"well hght-inhrt\">\n<p class=\"h3 mrgn-tp-0\">Express pick-up</p>\n<p class=\"h1 text-center\">2 to 9</p>\n<p class=\"h3 text-center\">business days</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-warning\">\n<p>We aren’t liable for any losses as a result of the passport not being issued to you or your child in time.</p>\n</div>\n<p>A passport officer will tell you the date of your pick-up when you apply.</p>\n<p>Learn more about <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/urgent-emergency-passport.html\">urgent or express passport services</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 passport-us\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<h2 id=\"passport-us\">Service standards for regular passport applications submitted from the US</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div class=\"row wb-eqht\">\n<div class=\"col-md-12 hght-inhrt\">\n<div class=\"well hght-inhrt\">\n<p class=\"h3 mrgn-tp-0 text-center\">Applications mailed from the US</p>\n<p class=\"h1 text-center\">20<sup id=\"fn3-rf\"><a class=\"fn-lnk\" href=\"#fn3\"><span class=\"wb-inv\">Footnote </span>*</a></sup></p>\n<p class=\"h3 text-center\">business days</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<aside class=\"wb-fnote\" role=\"note\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\" id=\"fn-2nd\">Footnotes</h2>\n<dl>\n<dt>Footnote *</dt>\n<dd id=\"fn3\">\n<p>This <strong>doesn’t</strong> include mailing time. Passports are printed in Canada, and mailing time varies by region. Because of this, you should give yourself extra time when applying. We aren’t liable for any losses if we can’t deliver your passport in time.</p>\n<p class=\"fn-rtn\"><a href=\"#fn3-rf\"><span class=\"wb-inv\">Return to footnote </span>*<span class=\"wb-inv\"> referrer</span></a></p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n</aside>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsgeneric_base_html mwsgeneric-base-html parbase\">\n<span data-incl-name=\"passport-cas-en\"></span>\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-bttm-sm\">Check your application status</h3>\n<p>Answer a few questions to find out how to check your application status.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/check-passport-travel-document-application.html\">Learn how to check the status of your application</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsgeneric_base_html mwsgeneric-base-html parbase\">\n<span data-incl-name=\"passport-ss-refund-en\"></span>\n<p class=\"h3\">If we don’t meet our service standards</p>\n<p>You may be eligible for a partial refund of some of your fees under the <a href=\"https://laws-lois.justice.gc.ca/eng/acts/S-8.4/\">Service Fees Act</a>. Refunds are processed automatically. Learn <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/fees/passport-travel-document-refunds.html\">what refunds you might be eligible for</a>.</p>\n<p>Learn more about our policies for fee remissions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/mandate/policies-operational-instructions-agreements/remissions-policy-service-fees-act.html\">Departmental Remission Policy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/mandate/policies-operational-instructions-agreements/remissions-policy-service-fees-act/passport-subordinate-remission-policy.html\">Passport Subordinate Remission Policy</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 passport-abroad\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<h2 id=\"passport-abroad\">Service standards for regular passport applications submitted outside Canada and the US</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div class=\"row wb-eqht\">\n<div class=\"col-md-12 hght-inhrt\">\n<div class=\"well hght-inhrt\">\n<p class=\"h3 mrgn-tp-0 text-center\">Applications mailed from abroad</p>\n<p class=\"h1 text-center\">20<sup id=\"fn4-rf\"><a class=\"fn-lnk\" href=\"#fn4\"><span class=\"wb-inv\">Footnote </span>*</a></sup></p>\n<p class=\"h3 text-center\">business days</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<aside class=\"wb-fnote\" role=\"note\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\" id=\"fn-3rd\">Footnotes</h2>\n<dl>\n<dt>Footnote *</dt>\n<dd id=\"fn4\">\n<p>This <strong>doesn’t</strong> include mailing time. Passports are printed in Canada, and mailing time varies by region. Because of this, you should give yourself extra time when applying. We aren’t liable for any losses if we can’t deliver your passport in time.</p>\n<p class=\"fn-rtn\"><a href=\"#fn4-rf\"><span class=\"wb-inv\">Return to footnote </span>*<span class=\"wb-inv\"> referrer</span></a></p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n</aside>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsgeneric_base_html mwsgeneric-base-html parbase\">\n<span data-incl-name=\"passport-cas-en\"></span>\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-bttm-sm\">Check your application status</h3>\n<p>Answer a few questions to find out how to check your application status.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/check-passport-travel-document-application.html\">Learn how to check the status of your application</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsgeneric_base_html mwsgeneric-base-html parbase\">\n<span data-incl-name=\"passport-ss-refund-en\"></span>\n<p class=\"h3\">If we don’t meet our service standards</p>\n<p>You may be eligible for a partial refund of some of your fees under the <a href=\"https://laws-lois.justice.gc.ca/eng/acts/S-8.4/\">Service Fees Act</a>. Refunds are processed automatically. Learn <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/fees/passport-travel-document-refunds.html\">what refunds you might be eligible for</a>.</p>\n<p>Learn more about our policies for fee remissions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/mandate/policies-operational-instructions-agreements/remissions-policy-service-fees-act.html\">Departmental Remission Policy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/mandate/policies-operational-instructions-agreements/remissions-policy-service-fees-act/passport-subordinate-remission-policy.html\">Passport Subordinate Remission Policy</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 td-reg\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<h2 id=\"td-reg\">Service standards for other travel document applications</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<p>We aim to process applications within our service standard.</p>\n<p>If you have already applied and now need a travel document urgently, <a aria-controls=\"centred-popup1\" class=\"wb-lbx\" href=\"#centred-popup1\">contact us</a>. We aim to respond to urgent requests sent through our web form within 3 business days.</p>\n<p>We recommend you <strong>don’t finalize any travel plans</strong> until you get your travel document.</p>\n<div class=\"row wb-eqht\">\n<div class=\"col-md-12 hght-inhrt\">\n<div class=\"well hght-inhrt\">\n<p class=\"h3 mrgn-tp-0 text-center\">Refugee travel documents and certificates of identity</p>\n<p class=\"h1 text-center\">20<sup id=\"fn5-rf\"><a class=\"fn-lnk\" href=\"#fn5\"><span class=\"wb-inv\">Footnote </span>*</a></sup></p>\n<p class=\"h3 text-center\">business days</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<aside class=\"wb-fnote\" role=\"note\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\" id=\"fn-4th\">Footnotes</h2>\n<dl>\n<dt>Footnote *</dt>\n<dd id=\"fn5\">\n<p>This <strong>doesn’t</strong> include mailing time. We aren’t liable for any losses if we can’t deliver your travel document in time.</p>\n<p class=\"fn-rtn\"><a href=\"#fn5-rf\"><span class=\"wb-inv\">Return to footnote </span>*<span class=\"wb-inv\"> referrer</span></a></p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n</aside>\n<section class=\"mfp-hide modal-dialog modal-content overlay-def\" id=\"centred-popup1\">\n<header class=\"modal-header\">\n<h2 class=\"modal-title\">Tell us if your travel document application is now urgent</h2>\n</header>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n<p><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/contact-ircc/web-form.html\">Fill out our web form</a>.</p>\n<p>Tell us it’s about a <strong>Certificate of Identity/Refugee Travel Document</strong>.</p>\n<p>Include your travel date and the reason you need the travel document.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsgeneric_base_html mwsgeneric-base-html parbase\">\n<span data-incl-name=\"passport-ss-refund-en\"></span>\n<p class=\"h3\">If we don’t meet our service standards</p>\n<p>You may be eligible for a partial refund of some of your fees under the <a href=\"https://laws-lois.justice.gc.ca/eng/acts/S-8.4/\">Service Fees Act</a>. Refunds are processed automatically. Learn <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/fees/passport-travel-document-refunds.html\">what refunds you might be eligible for</a>.</p>\n<p>Learn more about our policies for fee remissions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/mandate/policies-operational-instructions-agreements/remissions-policy-service-fees-act.html\">Departmental Remission Policy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/mandate/policies-operational-instructions-agreements/remissions-policy-service-fees-act/passport-subordinate-remission-policy.html\">Passport Subordinate Remission Policy</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 passport-official\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<h2>Service standards for official travel applications</h2>\n<p><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/official-travel/processing-times-special-diplomatic-passport.html\">Learn what our service standards are for official travel.</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 certified-other\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<h2 id=\"certified-other\">Certified true copies of passports or other travel documents</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div class=\"row wb-eqht\">\n<div class=\"col-md-12 hght-inhrt\">\n<div class=\"well hght-inhrt\">\n<p class=\"h1 text-center\">10<sup id=\"fn6-rf\"><a class=\"fn-lnk\" href=\"#fn6\"><span class=\"wb-inv\">Footnote </span>*</a></sup></p>\n<p class=\"h3 text-center\">business days</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<aside class=\"wb-fnote\" role=\"note\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\" id=\"fn-5th\">Footnotes</h2>\n<dl>\n<dt>Footnote *</dt>\n<dd id=\"fn6\">\n<p>This <strong>doesn’t</strong> include mailing time. We aren’t liable for any losses if we can’t deliver your copy in time.</p>\n<p class=\"fn-rtn\"><a href=\"#fn6-rf\"><span class=\"wb-inv\">Return to footnote </span>*<span class=\"wb-inv\"> referrer</span></a></p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n</aside>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsmediaplayer\">\n<div id=\"ccr-reference\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<section class=\"pagedetails\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Page details</h2>\n<gcds-date-modified>\n\t2025-06-25\n</gcds-date-modified>\n</section>\n</main>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n<div class=\"global-footer\">\n<footer id=\"wb-info\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">About this site</h2>\n<div class=\"gc-contextual\"><div class=\"container\">\n<nav>\n<h3>Canadian passports and other travel documents</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-col-xs-1 list-col-sm-2 list-col-md-3\">\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/help-centre.html\">Help Centre</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-passports/contact-passport-program.html\">Contact us</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"gc-main-footer\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<nav>\n<h3>Government of Canada</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-col-xs-1 list-col-sm-2 list-col-md-3\">\n<li><a href=\"/en/contact.html\">All contacts</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/government/dept.html\">Departments and agencies</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/government/system.html\">About government</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4><span class=\"wb-inv\">Themes and topics</span></h4>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled colcount-sm-2 colcount-md-3\">\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/jobs.html\">Jobs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/immigration-citizenship.html\">Immigration and citizenship</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://travel.gc.ca/\">Travel and tourism</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/business.html\">Business</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/benefits.html\">Benefits</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/health.html\">Health</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/taxes.html\">Taxes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/environment.html\">Environment and natural resources</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/defence.html\">National security and defence</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/culture.html\">Culture, history and sport</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/policing.html\">Policing, justice and emergencies</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/transport.html\">Transport and infrastructure</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.international.gc.ca/world-monde/index.aspx?lang=eng\">Canada and the world</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/finance.html\">Money and finances</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/science.html\">Science and innovation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/indigenous-peoples.html\">Indigenous Peoples</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/veterans-military.html\">Veterans and military</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/youth.html\">Youth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/life-events.html\">Manage life events</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"gc-sub-footer\">\n<div class=\"container d-flex align-items-center\">\n<nav>\n<h3 class=\"wb-inv\">Government of Canada Corporate</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/social.html\">Social media</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/mobile.html\">Mobile applications</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/government/about-canada-ca.html\">About Canada.ca</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/transparency/terms.html\">Terms and conditions</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/transparency/privacy.html\">Privacy</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n<div class=\"wtrmrk align-self-end\">\n<img alt=\"Symbol of the Government of Canada\" src=\"/etc/designs/canada/wet-boew/assets/wmms-blk.svg\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</footer>\n</div>\n</div>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">_satellite.pageBottom();</script>\n<script crossorigin=\"anonymous\" integrity=\"sha256-BbhdlvQf/xTY9gja0Dq3HiwQF8LaCRTXxZKRutelT44=\" src=\"//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.2.4/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/etc/designs/canada/wet-boew/js/ep-pp.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/etc/designs/canada/wet-boew/js/wet-boew.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/etc/designs/canada/wet-boew/js/theme.min.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}